图片来源：新华社记者 |牛其昌“ 经调查，洗马镇政府代收劳务公司隔离费用的情况属实，该行为系行为错误，钱已返还，并给予涉事副镇长马某免职处理。
Source: Xinhua News Agency & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45
”针对火神山援建者回乡被收隔离费一事，浠水县新型冠状病毒感染的肺炎疫情防控指挥部2020年3月7日发布《情况说明》称，情况属实，钱款已退还劳务公司。
It is true that the money has been returned to the service company according to the information note issued on 7 March 2020 by the Pneumonia Control Command of these new coronavirus infections in these counties.
另外，经浠水县委研究决定，对洗马镇负责隔离点工作的党委委员、副镇长马金安同志给予免职处理。
It is further indicated that it is decided that Comrade Ma Jinan, a member of the party committee and deputy mayor who is responsible for working in the area.
近日，一份落款为湖北浠水县洗马镇人民政府的证明文件引发关注。
It is indicated that the supporting documents of the people's government of these area are concerned recently.
该证明称，今收到2名火神山援建工作者集中隔离费4200元(150元/天/人)。
According to the certificate, we have received 4200 yuan (150 yuan per day / person) from two Fire Goddess Mountain construction workers.
此款由镇政府代收，用于支付在宾馆的隔离费用。
The money is collected by the township government to cover the cost of isolation in the hotel.
援建者王某此前在接受上游新闻采访时表示，1月31日，同学岑某带着他和另外3名工友，从浠水老家来到火神山医院建设现场。
In an interview with the upstream press it is indicated that on January 31 the student Cenmou with him and three other staff members came to the construction site from their home area at Mount Poplar Hospital.
他们5人给卫生间洁具打胶，总共干了3个白班、3个夜班。
They 5 people to toilet cleaning utensils glue, did a total of 3 day shift, 3 night shift.
干完活后，另3名工友于2月9日回到浠水，住进酒店隔离。
It is indicated that it is indicated that these 3 workmates should come back to these area on 9 February and live in isolation.
因他在武汉有房，他便和岑某留在武汉隔离。
Because he has a room in Wuhan, he and Cenmou stay in Wuhan isolation.
2月21日，王某和岑某回到浠水县洗马镇，随后被安排住进镇上“不见不散”宾馆。
It is indicated that on 21 February Wang and Cenmou have returned to these area and are subsequently arranged to live at these locations.
3月4日，值守宾馆的镇干部通知他，要按200元/天的标准收取隔离费。
On 4 March, the town official on duty at the hotel informed him that the quarantine fee would be charged at the rate of 200 yuan per day.
尽管王某多次向镇干部反映自己是援建者，黄冈市新冠肺炎疫情防控工作指挥部说可以不交，但洗马镇相关负责人仍坚持其必须交纳隔离费。
Although Wang has repeatedly complained to town cadres that he is a builder, the Huanggang New Crown Pneumonia Control and Prevention Command said that can not pay, but the relevant officials in the town still insist that they must pay the quarantine fee.
3月6日，根据网友发布的证明文件显示，湖北黄冈浠水洗马镇开出的证明称：“今收到火神山援建工作者岑某等2人回浠集中隔离费共计肆仟贰佰元整(￥4200)(150元/天/人)。
According to documents issued by net friends on March 6, it is indicated that these two people ($150 / day / person) are paying for the isolation fee for their climate change activities.
此款由镇政府代收，由武汉今润世家建筑劳务有限公司直接转入浠水县洗马镇财政所农村会计服务中心账户，用于支付岑某、王某在不见不散宾馆的隔离费用。
It is collected by the township government and transferred directly by Wuhan Run Family Construction Services Co. Ltd. to the account of Rural Accounting Service Centre at Zima Town Finance Institute in Sheshui County to pay the isolation fee of Shen Mou and Wang Mou at the hotel.
”该证明随即在网上引发关注，援建火神山后回乡集中隔离，是否应该自付隔离费也引发网友热议。
The certificate sparked online concern about whether people should pay their own quarantine fees to help build the mountain of Flamingo.
3月7日，据浠水县新型冠状病毒感染的肺炎疫情防控指挥部发布的《情况说明》，事件发生后，浠水县委、县政府迅速成立由县纪委、县委宣传部、县公安局组成的联合调查组。
It is indicated that it is indicated that after these incidents it is indicated that the joint investigation group consisting of the county disciplinary committee, the county promotion department and the county public security bureau is rapidly formed.
经调查，洗马镇政府代收劳务公司隔离费用的情况属实，行为是错误的，反映浠水县执行疫情防控政策不严、作风不实，深感自责和愧疚。
It is believed that the segregation fee of these companies is true and the behavior is wrong. It is indicated that the behavior reflects that the policies of prevention and control of these diseases are lax and untrue, and that they are guilty of self-reproach and guilt.
该笔代收费用已于3月7日上午退还劳务公司，并向当事人道歉。
The charge was returned to the company on the morning of March 7 and the party apologized.
《情况说明》称，浠水县洗马镇参建“两山”医院人员岑某和王某于2月21日从武汉返浠，按照疫情防控相关要求，两人返浠后安排到县“不见不散”宾馆集中隔离点隔离14天。
It is indicated that it is indicated that Shen Mou and Wang who were involved in the construction of these structures at these sites on February 21 would be separated from each other for 14 days in accordance with the requirements of the disease prevention and control.
两人在参建期间，中建三局已比照国家法定假日工资标准支付相关报酬。
The two men in the construction period, China Construction Bureau has been the national statutory holiday pay standards to pay the relevant remuneration.
同时，中建三局另按照每人每天300元的标准发放隔离补贴费用，按照15天计算，每人共计发放4500元。
At the same time, China Construction Bureau will also pay the isolation subsidy according to the standard of 300 yuan per person per day, calculated on the basis of 15 days, a total of 4,500 yuan.
洗马镇在两人隔离期间按照每人每天150元标准代收隔离期间食宿等费用，共计代收4200元，其他超出费用由镇政府承担，代收费用由武汉今润世家建筑劳务有限公司直接拨付到洗马镇会计服务中心。
During the period of separation, the town collected 4,200 yuan for board and lodging according to the standard of 150 yuan per person per day, and other expenses were borne by the township government.
《情况说明》还表示，深刻汲取此次事件的教训，举一反三，进一步查找工作中存在的短板和不足。
The Information Note also indicated that the lessons learned from the incident had been drawn in depth and that further work was needed to identify gaps and shortcomings.
经排查，全县其他参加武汉“两山”医院建设的返乡隔离人员，没有向个人收取费用。
After sorting out, the other county participated in Wuhan "two mountains" hospital construction of home quarantine personnel, no individual charges.
对洗马镇其他相关责任人员，将根据调查情况，依纪依法给予严肃处理。
Other responsible personnel in the town will be dealt with seriously according to law and discipline according to the investigation.
